  "guardrails": [
    "Every world gets its own settings.cfg; do not share detail settings between Morrowind and ESM4 worlds.",
    "Use --replace config --config <profile-dir> for launches so ambient user config cannot re-add Morrowind data/content.",
    "Generated openmw.cfg files use replace=data, replace=fallback-archive, and replace=content.",
    "Generated openmw.cfg files set user-data to a profile-local userdata directory.",
